title: Steve Ditko's 160-Page Package
description:
'Steve Ditko's 160-Page Package'

Published by Robyn Snyder and Steve Ditko, 1999, 160 pages

Written and Illustrated by Steve Ditko

Tales of suspense, action and adventure from the mind that co-created Spider-Man.

This "package" contains all new stories.

Fragments 26 pages
Contradiction 9 pages
Tsk! Tsk! 1 page
Faces 8 pages
Tsk! Tsk! 1 page
The Animal 6 pages
Ownership 15 pages
Variations on a Theme - Starter/Finisher 11 pages
Variations on a Theme 1 page
Tsk! Tsk! - The Foul Mouth 3 pages
Lift My Veil 6 pages
Shocker 9 pages
The Avenging World 5 pages
The Blabber Mouth Experience vs The 1st Hand Experience 

And many more. That was up to page 100 or so.
